ing: 2 (3 ounce) packages instant vanilla pudding mix
1 (16 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
des: "A lovely vanilla flavored dip for fresh fruit.  A friend shared this recipe with me.   Especially good with strawberries, pineapple and bananas."
ins: In a medium bowl, mix together the vanilla pudding mix, milk and amaretto liqueur. Beat in the thawed frozen whipped topping. Chill 1 hour in the refrigerator before serving.
